                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "H1JGjm",
                  "name": "artBodyContent",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 20,
                  "padding": [
                    32,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "EmP9x",
                      "fill": "$foreground-primary",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "The defending national champions have announced their full roster for the upcoming 2025 MCLA season, and the news has sent shockwaves through the club lacrosse community: all five of last year's All-Americans are returning.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Kh6eI",
                      "fill": "$foreground-secondary",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "In a sport where graduation and transfer attrition can reshape a program overnight, this level of continuity is virtually unprecedented at the elite level. Head coach Marcus Williams confirmed the roster on Tuesday, noting that the team's commitment to another championship run was \"unanimous\" from day one of the offseason.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "eg4W2",
                      "name": "artPullQuote",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "Iym1E",
                          "name": "artPullQuoteBorder",
                          "width": 4,
                          "height": "fill_container",
                          "fill": "$accent-gold"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "j49c6i",
                          "name": "artPullQuoteText",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "layout": "vertical",
                          "gap": 8,
                          "padding": [
                            16,
                            20
                          ],
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "b9hcjm",
                              "fill": "$foreground-primary",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "\"The commitment from this group was unanimous. We have unfinished business and everyone knows it.\"",
                              "lineHeight": 1.2,
                              "fontFamily": "$font-heading",
                              "fontSize": 24,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "s9AE9",
                              "fill": "$foreground-secondary",
                              "content": "— Coach Marcus Williams",
                              "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                              "fontSize": 13,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "AU2vg",
                      "fill": "$foreground-secondary",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "The team finished last season with a 22-1 record, losing only in a controversial semifinal game that many analysts still debate. The returning core includes midfielder Jake Thornton, widely regarded as the best player in the MCLA, along with four-time All-Conference attackman Ryan Bellows.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "IehOo",
                      "name": "inArticleAd",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "height": 90,
                      "fill": "$surface-card",
                      "cornerRadius": "$radius-sm",
                      "stroke": {
                        "align": "inside",
                        "thickness": 1,
                        "fill": "$surface-border"
                      },
                      "justifyContent": "center",
                      "alignItems": "center",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "kkvW0",
                          "fill": "$foreground-muted",
                          "content": "Advertisement — 728×90 Leaderboard",
                          "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                          "fontSize": 12,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "ZlLrg",
                      "fill": "$foreground-secondary",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Conference opponents have already begun adjusting their spring preparation schedules in response. \"You have to game-plan for them differently when they've got that kind of continuity,\" said one competing head coach who asked not to be named. \"They basically have a two-year head start on everyone else.\"",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
